  Title: The Man of Many Qualities
  By: R. G. H. Siu
  Locus:
    Hexagram: "9 - ䷈ - Ch'u"
    Line: 3
    Page: 68
By: Dio Chrysostom
---
Like men with sore eyes： they find the light painful, while the darkness,
which permits them to see nothing, is restful and agreeable.
